      "text": "This app estimates the body temperature by pulse rate, because the fever have effects on heart rate. To calculate the number of heart beats it use the main camera, in fact placing and keeping your index finger on the rear camera lens, making sure the finger is illuminated by camera flash (better method is cover with your finger both camera and flash), is able to count the beats by analyzing the color change due to finger pulsations.\n It's not a very accurate method, but it can be useful when you do not have a real thermometer.\nWe recommend the use of a real thermometer.",
